title: Help me! Uspecified error occurred please check logs for more information! (MACBOOK PRO)
body:
So guys, 
I have recently just had a thunderstorm and my internet went down. That was yesterday. So today I tried to open my Lol application, but then it said "Unspecified error occurred please check logs for more information". Therefore now I can't open my lol on my mac! PLEASE HELP ME!!!!!

replies.body: i have the exact same problem dude... please riot help us
omg it worked i love u
which one? i need to know! which players solution worked the best?! HELP ME
ME TOO IM TRYING TO FIND A STUPID SOLUTION BUT NO THE INTERNET WONT SHOW ME A STUPID SOLUTION TT^TT
I can't log in just says connection error.
Yep. At least in Help & Support I'm seeing more people having my issue. Glad it ain't just me :)
